    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✯ PRESENTATION ✯</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Night of the Stars</strong> is a 2D exciting RPG full of secrets and sidequests in the style of Aldorlea games such as <i>Millennium</i> or <i>Dreamscape</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✯ SUMMARY ✯</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every 888 years in Faust, it's the ☆ Night of the Stars ☆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've been chosen by your community to reach out for the 3 Half-Gods and stop the ever-expanding Void from swallowing every life form. Your salvation lies in the joint power of the Half-Gods. But will they even want to collaborate with you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a Destroyer and a Chaos among their ranks, nothing is less certain. You'll have to use not only your might, but also your wits. Past records of history, now almost forgotten, have proven it's not a given, and the Champion sometimes struggle to reach his goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But you have to succeed. There is no other option. And you only have 24 hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Because tonight is not your ordinary day... for you and everyone else, it's the Night of the Stars! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✯ FEATURES ✯</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ✦ Visible Enemies </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ✦ Mouse Control</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ✦ Autosave after each battle</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ✦ Evolving &amp; Strategic skills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ✦ A lot of interactivity and many secrets rewarding exploration</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ✦ 2 Different Endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ✦ 5 modes of difficulty</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ✦ 15-20 hours of playtime </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ✦ 15 secret rooms</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ✦ 21 sidequests (+ main quests)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ✦ 21 unique relics to find</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ✦ 50+ enemies</p>",
